OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy for a time with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain moving south across
OL,7,Fthe region, the rain mostly light.
OL,8,FHowever, turning drier and brighter
OL,9,Flater on this morning, with sunny
OL,10,Fspells developing. A few showers
OL,11,Fpossible into the afternoon. Feeling
OL,12,Fcold.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FClearer, with any showers
OL,15,Fmostly fading during the early
OL,16,Fevening. However, further showers will
OL,17,Farrive from the northwest heading into
OL,18,Fthe night. Turning increasingly
OL,19,Fblustery and feeling cold.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
